<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
 <head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta content="IE=edge" http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible"/>
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport"/>
  <title>
   Just A Pinch Recipes
  </title>
  <!-- Bootstrap -->
  <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
   html, body {
            font-family: "Trebuchet MS", 'Trebuchet', Verdana, sans;

            background: #fcfbf2; /* Old browsers */
            background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #fcfbf2 0%, #efecda 100%); /* FF3.6+ */
            background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0%, #fcfbf2), color-stop(100%, #efecda)); /* Chrome,Safari4+ */
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #fcfbf2 0%, #efecda 100%); /* Chrome10+,Safari5.1+ */
            background: -o-linear-gradient(top, #fcfbf2 0%, #efecda 100%); /* Opera 11.10+ */
            background: -ms-linear-gradient(top, #fcfbf2 0%, #efecda 100%); /* IE10+ */
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fcfbf2 0%, #efecda 100%); /* W3C */
            filter: progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.gradient(startColorstr='#fcfbf2', endColorstr='#efecda', GradientType=0); /* IE6-9 */

            background-image: url('data:image/gif;base64,');

        }

        h3 {
            color: #bf1e2e;
        }

        #logo {
            margin: 12px;
            background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat;
            width: 187;
            height: 44px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-indent: -999em;
        }

        #lady-graphic {
            background: url(data:image/png;base64,) no-repeat;
            width: 130px;
            height: 175px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-right: 40px;
            float: left;
        }

        .icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
        }

        .pinterest-icon {
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
        }

        .facebook-icon {
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
        }

        .code {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {

            .container {
                width: 700px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 20px;
                background: #fff;
                border: 1px solid #eee;
                -moz-box-shadow: -5px 5px 10px #888;
                -webkit-box-shadow: -5px 5px 10px #888;
                box-shadow: -5px 5px 10px #888;

                background: #ffffff; /* Old browsers */
                background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #fcfff4 63%, #e9e9ce 100%); /* FF3.6+ */
                background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0%, #ffffff), color-stop(63%, #fcfff4), color-stop(100%, #e9e9ce)); /* Chrome,Safari4+ */
                background: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #fcfff4 63%, #e9e9ce 100%); /* Chrome10+,Safari5.1+ */
                background: -o-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #fcfff4 63%, #e9e9ce 100%); /* Opera 11.10+ */
                background: -ms-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #fcfff4 63%, #e9e9ce 100%); /* IE10+ */
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #fcfff4 63%, #e9e9ce 100%); /* W3C */
                filter: progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.gradient(startColorstr='#ffffff', endColorstr='#e9e9ce', GradientType=0); /* IE6-9 */
            }

            #logo {
                background: url(data:image/png;base64,);
                width: 357px;
                height: 91px;
            }
        }
  </style>
  <!-- HTML5 Shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
  <!-- WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file:// -->
  <!--[if lt IE 9]&gt;
    &lt;script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
    &lt;script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
    &lt;![endif]-->
 </head>
 <body>
  <div class="container">
   <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
     <div id="logo">
      Just A Pinch Recipes
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
   <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-3 hidden-xs">
     <div id="lady-graphic">
     </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-9">
     <h3>
      Oops!
     </h3>
     <p class="lead">
      Well sugar... looks like it got a little too hot in the Test Kitchen and our hosting company blew a fuse. They're working on fixing the issue and we hope to be up and running shortly.
     </p>
     <p class="lead">
      Sorry for any inconvenience!
     </p>
     <!--&lt;h3&gt;We're sorry. We need to take a moment here.&lt;/h3&gt;

            &lt;p&gt;We are performing maintenance to improve your Just A Pinch experience. Things should be cooking again soon.&lt;/p&gt;
            -->
     <div style="clear:both;">
      <hr/>
     </div>
     <div id="links">
      In the meantime, care to visit us on
      <a class="btn btn-default" href="http://www.facebook.com/justapinch" target="_blank">
       <div class="icon facebook-icon">
       </div>
       Facebook
      </a>
      or
      <a class="btn btn-default" href="http://pinterest.com/justapinchcooks/" target="_blank">
       <div class="icon pinterest-icon">
       </div>
       Pinterest
      </a>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </body>
</html>
